nave\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"host taekwondo\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Originally built in three years by a crew of just 1,500 and overseen by four architects for the1900 World's Fair, the scale and scope of the refurbishment now in the hands of Fran\\u00e7ois Chatillon is staggering.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"a crew\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"four architects\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"the1900 World's Fair\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"the scale\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"scope\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"the refurbishment\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the hands\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"Fran\\u00e7ois Chatillon\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a recent interview with theFinancial Times, the architect shared that he's working with no fewer than 50 companies and 200 subcontractors.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recent interview\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"theFinancial Times\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"the architect\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"no fewer than 50 companies\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"200 subcontractors\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, even a seemingly simple task like choosing a shade of concrete for the nave's floor took three months.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"even a seemingly simple task\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"a shade\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"concrete\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"the nave's floor\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"three months\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The project's full scope includes unifying its galleries and naves, rehabilitating its balconies and cantilevered concrete walkway, replacing walls and partitions added over the years with transparent glass panes, and restoring period details like the bronze adornments on the main nave'sgrandstaircase.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The project's full scope\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"its galleries\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"naves\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"its balconies\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"cantilevered concrete walkway\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"walls\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"partitions\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"transparent glass panes\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"period details\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze adornments\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"the main nave'sgrandstaircase\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's little wonder that the project has been in the works since 2021.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"little wonder\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the works\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even before it shuttered, theGrandPalaishad cultivated a reputation for captivating gutsy, outside-the-box thinkers.Anish KapoorandKarl Lagerfeldpushed the 188,000-square-foot dome's spatial boundaries with Kapoor'sLeviathansculpture and Lagerfeld's larger-than-life rocket for Chanel's Fall/Winter 2017 runway show).\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1934, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chanel\", \"score\": 0.9999359752765814, \"rank\": 6.402882282232428e-05, \"text\": \"Chanel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chanel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chanel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theGrandPalaishad\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"a reputation\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"gutsy\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"the-box\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"Anish KapoorandKarl\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the 188,000-square-foot dome's spatial boundaries\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"Kapoor'sLeviathansculpture\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon its full completion in 2025, the fully restoredPalaiswill welcome 60,000 plants in a sprawling landscape inspired by the neighboring Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es gardens, and two of its galleries will host the collections of the Centre Pompidou while it undergoesrefurbishment.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9938637728104254, \"rank\": 0.005341849563968814, \"text\": \"Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its full completion\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"60,000 plants\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprawling landscape\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"its galleries\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"the collections\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"the Centre Pompidou\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The opportunity to redevelop an icon is amazing, but theGrandPalaisfeels like so much more,\\\" Chatillon says.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opportunity\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2260}, {\"ngram\": \"an icon\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"theGrandPalaisfeels\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"Chatillon\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the opportunity to return a permanent public use to the building, to redevelop the surrounding grounds, to connect the building back with the city, and to adapt it for the Olympics and future generations.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"a permanent public use\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"the surrounding grounds\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"future generations\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is truly a once-in-a-lifetime project.\\\"\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a-lifetime\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next Article Plus, new research on invasive rats' role in deforesting Easter Island, and Sarah Hoover memoir... Festive season is upon us, and Worthlessstudios sure has plenty to celebrate.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.999432470652784, \"rank\": 0.0004363999298112267, \"text\